    CLEAR : WA_FINAL, WA_BSID, WA_BKPF, WA_BSEG, WA_KNA1, WA_SKAT, WA_PAYR, WA_CSKT, WA_CEPCT, WA_CUSTBAL.
  ENDLOOP.

  SORT IT_FINAL ASCENDING BY KUNNR BUDAT BELNR.


